                              "text": "Bodyless Mode - Keymapping:\n\n1 -> HOME\n2 -> METERS\n3 -> ROUTING\n4 -> LIBRARY\n5 -> EFFECT\n6 -> SETUP\n7 -> MONITOR\n8 -> SCENES\n9 -> MUTE GRP\n0 -> UTILITY\n\narrow keys -> up, down, left, right\nQ..Z -> Encoder++\nA..H -> Encoder--\nY..N -> Encoder Buttons",
